reg add HKCU\Environment /v PYTHONPATH /d "C:\Python27;C:\PYCOM\bin;C:\PYCOM\py_srcroot;C:\PYCOM\qtp" /f
ECHO user environment variable for PYTHONPATH has been set successfully

